			<abstract label="Abstract:">Scrapbooks, photographs, and volumes of bird observation
				notes. Also, 18 notebooks of Verdi Burtch's and Clarence Stone's bird observations
				and a catalog of bird and plant photographs arranged by species.</abstract>
			<langmaterial label="Language:">Collection material in <language encodinganalog="041" langcode="eng">English</language></langmaterial>
		</did>
		<bioghist encodinganalog="MARC 545">
			<head altrender="biography" id="a2">BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE </head>
			<p>Verdi Burtch was an ornithologist in Penn Yan, Yates County, New York.</p>
		</bioghist>
		<scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
			<head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
			<p>Scrapbooks, photographs, and volumes of bird observation notes. Also, 18 notebooks of
				Verdi Burtch's and Clarence Stone's bird observations and a catalog of bird and
				plant photographs arranged by species.</p>
		</scopecontent>
